{"title": "How Do I Share Medications to a Patient with the MediRecords App?", "body": "Follow these steps to share Medications to a patient with the MediRecords App:\nCurrent Rx:\nOpen the Patient Record.\nNavigate to the Clinical tab.\nOn the left-hand column scroll down and select Medications.\nSelect the Current Rx tab, if not selected;\nSelect the New Rx to start prescribing.\nFill out all the fields as per normal when Prescribing, you are find steps on how-to Prescribe here: How to Create an Electronic Prescription\nAt the end of Prescribing a new Medication, you will click Prescribe and select any of these options.\nThese Medications will now appear in the Patient MediRecords App for the patient to access.\n "}